<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Split Payment — Medium-Fidelity Wireframe Prototype</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --bg: #F5F3EE;
    --surface: #FFFFFF;
    --border: #D6D2C8;
    --border-strong: #A8A39A;
    --text-primary: #1A1917;
    --text-secondary: #6B6760;
    --text-hint: #A8A39A;
    --accent: #1B4FD8;
    --accent-light: #EBF0FD;
    --accent-text: #0F2E8A;
    --success: #1A6B3A;
    --success-bg: #E8F5EE;
    --warning: #7A4A00;
    --warning-bg: #FEF3DC;
    --annotation: #8B3A3A;
    --annotation-bg: #FDF0F0;
    --annotation-border: #E8C5C5;
    --screen-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.10), 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    --font: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    --mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }

  body {
    font-family: var(--font);
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    padding: 40px 24px;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .page-content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .page-header p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .screen-section {
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .screen-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .screen-number {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .screen-label h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .screen-label span {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    background: var(--border);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .screen-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    gap: 28px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .screen-wrapper.pos-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 680px 280px;
  }
  .screen-wrapper.mobile-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .device-frame {
    box-shadow: var(--screen-shadow);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--surface);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
  }

  .device-frame.pos {
    min-height: 480px;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .device-frame.mobile {
    width: 300px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border-width: 6px;
    border-color: #2C2C2A;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .device-titlebar {
    background: #2A2A2A;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .device-titlebar .dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .device-titlebar .dot.r { background: #FF5F57; }
  .device-titlebar .dot.y { background: #FEBC2E; }
  .device-titlebar .dot.g { background: #28C840; }
  .device-titlebar .title { margin-left: 8px; opacity: 0.7; }

  .mobile-notch {
    background: #2C2C2A;
    height: 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 16px;
  }
  .mobile-notch .notch-bar {
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: #555;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .mobile-status {
    background: #1A1917;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 4px 16px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .screen-body {
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .screen-body.mobile-body {
    padding: 16px;
    min-height: 540px;
  }

  .pos-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pos-header .store-name {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .pos-header .total-amount {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  .pos-header .total-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .pos-badge {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--accent-text);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #C5D5F8;
  }

  .split-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .split-table th {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .split-table td {
    padding: 10px 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .split-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

  .status-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .status-pill.ready { background: var(--success-bg); color: var(--success); }
  .status-pill.pending { background: var(--warning-bg); color: var(--warning); }
  .status-pill.paid { background: var(--success-bg); color: var(--success); }
  .status-pill::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .status-pill.ready::before { background: var(--success); }
  .status-pill.pending::before { background: #E8A020; }
  .status-pill.paid::before { background: var(--success); }

  .amount-display {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .add-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1.5px dashed #C5D5F8;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .allocation-bar {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .allocation-bar .bar-track {
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .allocation-bar .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 0.3s;
  }
  .allocation-bar .bar-fill.full { background: var(--success); }
  .allocation-bar .bar-fill.partial { background: var(--accent); }
  .allocation-bar .bar-labels {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .allocation-bar .bar-labels strong { color: var(--text-primary); }

  .qr-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #FAFAF8;
  }
  .qr-visual {
    width: 80px; height: 80px;
    background: repeating-conic-gradient(#333 0% 25%, #fff 0% 50%) 0 0 / 8px 8px;
    border: 2px solid #333;
  }
  .qr-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .qr-label strong { color: var(--accent); }

  .btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: center;
    border: none;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
  }
  .btn.primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
  .btn.secondary { background: var(--surface); color: var(--text-primary); border: 1.5px solid var(--border-strong); }
  .btn.success { background: var(--success); color: #fff; }

  .progress-bar-block {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .progress-track {
    height: 20px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 8px;
  }
  .progress-segment {
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 8px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .progress-segment.seg1 { background: var(--success); }
  .progress-segment.seg2 { background: var(--border); }

  .payment-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .payment-row.approved { border-color: #A8D5B8; background: var(--success-bg); }
  .payment-row.pending { border-color: #F0D080; background: var(--warning-bg); }

  .still-owed {
    background: var(--text-primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .still-owed .amount { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; font-family: var(--mono); letter-spacing: -1px; }
  .still-owed .label { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.7; margin-top: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }

  .mobile-section-header {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .mobile-section-header:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

  .mobile-total-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 16px 0 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .mobile-total-header .amount { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; font-family: var(--mono); }
  .mobile-total-header .label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); }

  .mobile-pay-option {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .mobile-pay-option.selected { border-color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-light); }
  .radio-dot {
    width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-strong);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .radio-dot.active { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .radio-dot.active::after {
    content: '';
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .group-status {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border: 1px solid #C5D5F8;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .group-status .gs-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .group-status .gs-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .group-status .gs-label { color: var(--accent-text); }
  .group-status .gs-val { font-weight: 500; font-family: var(--mono); }

  .waiting-banner {
    background: var(--warning-bg);
    border: 1px solid #F0D080;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--warning);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .waiting-banner .pulse {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #E8A020;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .confirm-check {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--success-bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--success);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 12px;
    font-size: 24px;
  }
  .confirm-amount {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .confirm-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .confirm-detail-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 8px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .confirm-detail-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
  .confirm-detail-row .key { color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .confirm-detail-row .val { font-weight: 500; }

  .remaining-owed-mobile {
    background: var(--text-primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .remaining-owed-mobile .label { font-size: 11px; opacity: 0.6; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .remaining-owed-mobile .amount { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; font-family: var(--mono); }

  .annotation-panel {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .annotation {
    background: var(--annotation-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--annotation-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }
  .annotation .ann-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--annotation);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .annotation .ann-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #4A2020;
  }
  .annotation .ann-req {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    background: #E8C5C5;
    color: var(--annotation);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 40px 0;
  }

  .page-footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-hint);
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .screen-wrapper.pos-layout,
    .screen-wrapper.mobile-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .screen-wrapper.pos-layout .device-frame.pos {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-content">

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Split Payment — Medium-Fidelity Wireframe Prototype</h1>
  <p>CS 6750: Human-Computer Interaction &nbsp;·&nbsp; Richard Harris &nbsp;·&nbsp; Combined POS Terminal + Mobile Interface (Alt A + Alt C)</p>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SCREEN 1 — POS Split Planner (Pre-auth)
══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="screen-section">
  <div class="screen-label">
    <div class="screen-number">1</div>
    <h2>POS Terminal — Split Planner View</h2>
    <span>Pre-authorization</span>
  </div>

  <div class="screen-wrapper pos-layout">
    <div class="device-frame pos">
      <div class="device-titlebar">
        <span class="dot r"></span><span class="dot y"></span><span class="dot g"></span>
        <span class="title">RetailPOS v4.2 — Register 3</span>
      </div>
      <div class="screen-body">
        <div class="pos-header">
          <div>
            <div class="store-name">Transaction #4821</div>
            <div class="total-amount">$190.00</div>
            <div class="total-label">Total Due</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pos-badge">Split Payment Mode</div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 100px;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <div>
            <table class="split-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Name / Label</th>
                  <th>Amount</th>
                  <th>Share</th>
                  <th>Method</th>
                  <th>Status</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-weight:500;">Alex</td>
                  <td><span class="amount-display">$60.00</span></td>
                  <td style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:12px;">31.6%</td>
                  <td style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:12px;">Debit ****1234</td>
                  <td><span class="status-pill ready">Ready</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-weight:500;">Jordan</td>
                  <td><span class="amount-display">$80.00</span></td>
                  <td style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:12px;">42.1%</td>
                  <td style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:12px;">QR pending</td>
                  <td><span class="status-pill pending">Waiting</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-weight:500;">Sam</td>
                  <td><span class="amount-display">$50.00</span></td>
                  <td style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:12px;">26.3%</td>
                  <td style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:12px;">QR pending</td>
                  <td><span class="status-pill pending">Waiting</span></td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="add-row">+ Add payment method</div>
            <div class="allocation-bar">
              <div class="bar-track">
                <div class="bar-fill full" style="width:100%;"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="bar-labels">
                <span>Allocated: <strong>$190.00 (100%)</strong></span>
                <span>Remaining: <strong style="color:var(--success);">$0.00</strong></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="qr-block">
              <div class="qr-visual"></div>
              <div class="qr-label"><strong>Scan with your phone</strong><br>to pay your share</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="btn primary">Confirm Plan &amp; Begin Authorization</button>
        <button class="btn secondary">Cancel Split</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="annotation-panel">
      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 1</div>
        <div class="ann-text">The "Split Payment Mode" badge and dedicated planning screen provide a clear <strong>affordance</strong> for split payments — closing the Gulf of Execution identified in needfinding, where no visible entry point existed on standard POS screens.</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R1 — Pre-transaction planning</span>
      </div>
      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 2</div>
        <div class="ann-text">The allocation bar shows remaining balance in real time, eliminating manual arithmetic. This offloads the arithmetic task from the user's working memory entirely, satisfying Norman's principle of reducing cognitive load.</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R6 — Low cognitive load</span>
      </div>
      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 3</div>
        <div class="ann-text">The QR code includes an explicit instruction label — <em>"Scan with your phone to pay your share"</em> — directly addressing the QR ambiguity theme surfaced in the first evaluation (participants unsure whether it was a menu, ad, or payment link).</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R3 — Multi-party coordination</span>
      </div>
      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 4</div>
        <div class="ann-text">Row-based tabular layout allows the cashier to visually scan all payment participants and their statuses simultaneously — reducing the Gulf of Evaluation by making the full state of the transaction legible at a glance.</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R2 — Real-time feedback</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SCREEN 2 — POS In-Progress View
══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="screen-section">
  <div class="screen-label">
    <div class="screen-number">2</div>
    <h2>POS Terminal — In-Progress View</h2>
    <span>After first partial payment</span>
  </div>

  <div class="screen-wrapper pos-layout">
    <div class="device-frame pos">
      <div class="device-titlebar">
        <span class="dot r"></span><span class="dot y"></span><span class="dot g"></span>
        <span class="title">RetailPOS v4.2 — Register 3</span>
      </div>
      <div class="screen-body">
        <div class="pos-header">
          <div>
            <div class="store-name">Transaction #4821</div>
            <div class="total-amount">$190.00</div>
            <div class="total-label">Total Due</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pos-badge">1 of 3 Paid</div>
        </div>

        <div class="progress-bar-block">
          <div class="progress-track">
            <div style="display:flex;height:100%;">
              <div class="progress-segment seg1" style="width:31.5%;">$60 · 31.6%</div>
              <div class="progress-segment seg2" style="width:68.5%;color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;padding-left:10px;">$130 · 68.4% remaining</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">
            <span>$60.00 authorized (31.6%)</span>
            <span>$130.00 still owed (68.4%)</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <table class="split-table" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Participant</th><th>Amount</th><th>Share</th><th>Method</th><th>Status</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="font-weight:500;">Alex</td>
              <td><span class="amount-display">$60.00</span></td>
              <td style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">31.6%</td>
              <td style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">Debit ****1234</td>
              <td><span class="status-pill paid">Approved</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="font-weight:500;">Jordan</td>
              <td><span class="amount-display">$80.00</span></td>
              <td style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">42.1%</td>
              <td style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">QR — phone</td>
              <td><span class="status-pill pending">Waiting</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="font-weight:500;">Sam</td>
              <td><span class="amount-display">$50.00</span></td>
              <td style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">26.3%</td>
              <td style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);">QR — phone</td>
              <td><span class="status-pill pending">Waiting</span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="still-owed">
          <div class="label">Present next payment for</div>
          <div class="amount">$130.00</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;opacity:0.6;margin-top:4px;">68.4% of total remaining</div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;gap:8px;">
          <button class="btn secondary" style="font-size:12px;padding:8px;margin-bottom:0;">Adjust an amount</button>
          <button class="btn secondary" style="font-size:12px;padding:8px;margin-bottom:0;">Undo last payment</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="annotation-panel">
      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 5</div>
        <div class="ann-text">The segmented progress bar gives immediate visual feedback after each payment — users see exactly what portion of the total has been satisfied. This is the core fix for the Gulf of Evaluation gap: the system now communicates its internal state clearly.</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R2 — Real-time balance feedback</span>
      </div>
      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 6</div>
        <div class="ann-text">The large high-contrast "Present next payment for: $130.00" block dominates the lower half of the screen, giving the cashier and customer an unambiguous action prompt. This addresses Norman's principle: the system's current state should dictate the next action clearly.</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R2 + R6</span>
      </div>
      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 7</div>
        <div class="ann-text">"Adjust an amount" and "Undo last payment" buttons provide error recovery without voiding the entire transaction — a direct response to the evaluation finding that forced restarts were the most frustrating breakdown participants experienced.</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R4 — Error recovery</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

