      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 12</div>
        <div class="ann-text">The confirmation screen shows a receipt-level detail block with auth code and payment method — satisfying R5 (Transparent receipts) and closing the Gulf of Evaluation loop. The user has unambiguous evidence their payment was registered correctly.</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R5 — Transparent receipts</span>
      </div>
      <div class="annotation">
        <div class="ann-tag">Design Decision 13</div>
        <div class="ann-text">The group status panel persists on the confirmation screen — a direct fix for the "Waiting Game" theme from evaluation, where participants felt abandoned after submitting their own payment. They can now see exactly whose payment remains outstanding.</div>
        <span class="ann-req">R3 — Multi-party coordination</span>
